reviewText:
Great deal
Perfect disks
Quick shipping!
We will order more!
My son loves the show and having these dvds are perfect way for him to watch it.
I had to order this DVD two times.  Both times the DVD would not work.  It would not play beyond the opening previews.  Very disappointed!!!!
My parent patrons love Sid the Science Kid.  When they check out these movies their children have fun while secretly learning something.  The movie came in a timely manner and in great shape.
